MUSIC
──────────────────────────────────────────────
Default autoplay: “Killa Bees” — 8BFR
About page: “Earth Angel to Guardian Angel”
Dedication page: “Missing You”
Kids Zone: “Old School Rap”
All tracks hosted via Google Drive or Spotify preview embeds.

──────────────────────────────────────────────
MONETIZATION
──────────────────────────────────────────────
• Game coins, upgrades, gifts
• 20 % of paid song downloads to 8BFR
• 30 % of sticker pack sales to 8BFR
• Paid artist-studio upgrades
• Ad banner slots $5 / week
• Stripe for purchases / PayPal for donations
• Discount-code system connected to Supabase
• Transaction logs emailed to 8bfr.music@gmail.com

──────────────────────────────────────────────
INTEGRATIONS
──────────────────────────────────────────────
Supabase:
  • Auth (login, signup, OAuth Google + Apple)
  • Database (users, posts, songs, ads, coins, logs)
  • Storage (user media, mastered tracks, covers)

Stripe → shop, upgrades, ads  
PayPal → donations  
AI → lyrics, mastering, translation, album-cover image generation  
Games → HTML5 iframes under “Game Hub”  
Chat → Supabase real-time channel  
Eruda console → debug on mobile

──────────────────────────────────────────────
DESIGN + UI
──────────────────────────────────────────────
• Black / purple glow accent
• Circular floating hamburger menu (left-side, follows scroll)
• Ad banner scrolls horizontally with pause / manual control
• Clicking ad → opens popup iframe
• Featured Songs & Featured Artists from database
• Owner = 8bfr.music@gmail.com (auto-login for testing)
• Footer: affiliates, socials, back-to-top, “Need Help?” blink text

──────────────────────────────────────────────
AI FUNCTIONS
──────────────────────────────────────────────
Lyrics Generator, Mastering Enhancer, Album Cover Creator, Translation Tool  
All linked to OpenAI GPT-4o APIs through Supabase Edge Functions.

──────────────────────────────────────────────
ROLES & ACCESS
──────────────────────────────────────────────
Owner > Admin > Mod > Artist > User > Guest  
Owner Panel = full control / financial / approvals  
Admin Panel = content + user management  
Mod Panel = moderation + reports  
Artist Studio = upload + feature submission  
Public = radio + feed + games + shop

